NAME
	query_admin - test if a player is an admin

SYNOPSIS
	int query_admin(object arg)

DESCRIPTION
	Check if 'arg' is an admin player object.

RETURN VALUE
	Returns 1 if 'arg' is an admin player object, 0 otherwise.

EXAMPLES
	if (query_admin(this_player()) {
	   write("Welcome the mighty admin!\n");
	}

SEE ALSO
	safun/query_guest, safun/query_mortal, safun/query_user_type,
	safun/query_wizard
